export const profileData = {
  username: 'Jeremiah Warinner',
  quote: '"The only legitimate use of a computer is to play games." - Eugene Jarvis',
  linkedin: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jeremiah-warinner-8b162821a/',
  github: 'https://github.com/jeremiahwarinner',
  email: 'mailto:warinnerjeremiah@gmail.com',
};

export const projects = [
  {
    title: "Inbox Guardian",
    description: "Smart SMS spam filter for Android devices using AI and machine learning.",
    image: "/inbox.png",
    color: "bg-blue-100 text-blue-800",
    details: `Inbox Guardian is an SMS spam filter meant to be deployed in addition to any existing SMS application. It uses a logistic regression model, the BERT language model, and other holistic methods such as keyword recognition to flag spam messages with a tested 90% accuracy rate.`,
    link: "https://github.com/Lopezm0908/SMS-filtering",
    type: "mail"
  },
  {
    title: "SchedLite",
    description: "Intelligent Employee Scheduling Solution",
    image: "/schedule.png",
    color: "bg-green-100 text-green-800",
    details: `SchedLite is a comprehensive employee scheduling application that simplifies the complex task of managing work schedules. With features like automated schedule generation, skill-based shift assignments, and Excel export capabilities, it's the perfect tool for businesses of all sizes. From adding new employees and updating their skills to filling empty shifts and exporting schedules, ShiftMaster Pro offers a user-friendly interface to handle all your scheduling needs efficiently. Built with Python and backed by SQLite, this application combines powerful functionality with ease of use, making workforce management a breeze.`,
    link: "https://github.com/jeremiahwarinner/Schedule-Manager",
    type: "scheduling"
  },
  {
    title: "Major Employment and Salary Analysis Dashboard",
    description: "Empower your career decisions with data-driven insights on employment rates, salaries, and job market trends across various academic majors.",
    image: "/major.png",
    color: "bg-purple-100 text-purple-800",
    details: `A sophisticated, interactive dashboard that provides comprehensive analytics on employment and salary data across different academic majors. Built with Python, Dash, and Plotly, this tool offers dynamic visualizations of employment rates, salary distributions, and full-time year-round employment statistics.`,
    link: "https://github.com/jeremiahwarinner/Major-Employment-and-Salary-Analysis-Dashboard",
    type: "analysis"
  },
  {
    title: "Interactive Data-Driven Career Insights",
    description: "Uncover salary trends across industries, experience levels, and work arrangements to make informed career decisions.",
    image: "/visuals.png",
    color: "bg-red-100 text-red-800",
    details: `A comprehensive data analysis and visualization tool designed to illuminate salary trends in the modern job market. Using a rich dataset of 2024 salary information, this project offers valuable insights into compensation patterns across various job titles, experience levels, and remote work arrangements.`,
    link: "https://github.com/jeremiahwarinner/Salary-Trends-Visualizer",
    type: "data"
  }
];
